## Remarks

<span data-ttu-id="cb437-102">健康情況端點用來執行評估元件的健全狀況的健全狀況檢查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-102">Health endpoints are used to perform health checks that assess the health of a component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-103">健康情況端點可以用來：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-103">Health endpoints can be used to:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="cb437-104">通知刪除失敗的重大健全狀況檢查的處理序的協調流程工具。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-104">Notify orchestration tools to kill a process that is failing a critical health check.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="cb437-105">做為監視工具，透過追蹤和提供警示相關的早期問題指標的可用性和服務的效能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-105">Serve as an early problem indicator for monitoring tools by tracking and providing alerts about the the availability and performance of a service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="cb437-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior` 是 WCF 服務的行為擴充 IServiceBehavior 和衍生自<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior` is a WCF service behavior that extends IServiceBehavior and derives from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="cb437-107">新增`ServiceHealthBehavior`執行個體<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType>集合啟用下列：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-107">Adding a `ServiceHealthBehavior` instance to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType> collection enables the following:</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="cb437-108">**服務健全狀況的發行集：** 服務狀態，節流計數等的特定服務的詳細資訊，並可顯示容量使用的 HTTP/GET 要求，且`?health`查詢字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-108">**Publication of Service Health:** Service-specific details such as service state, throttle counts, and capacity can be displayed using an HTTP/GET request with the `?health` query string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-109">了解並輕鬆地顯示資訊的存取權最重要的是疑難排解行為不當的 WCF 服務時。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-109">Knowing and easily having access to the information displayed is of paramount importance when troubleshooting a misbehaving WCF service.</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="cb437-110">**傳回的 HTTP 回應碼：** 其中一個可以在查詢字串中指定 HTTP/GET 健全狀況探查要求的 HTTP 狀態碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-110">**Return of HTTP response codes:** One can specify in the query string the HTTP status code for an HTTP/GET health probe request.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="cb437-111">健康情況端點才有意義，它會監視其健康狀態的元件內容中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-111">A health endpoint is only meaningful in the context of the component whose health it monitors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-112">它沒有任何其他的意義或用途。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-112">It has no other meaning or purpose.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-113">因此，其健康狀態會是元件的健全狀況的管道。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-113">As such, its health is a conduit to the health of the component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-114">用戶端*應該*假設適用於整個元件健康情況端點所傳回的 HTTP 回應碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-114">Clients *should* assume that the HTTP response code returned by the health endpoint is applicable to the entire component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-115">這是與目前基礎結構的工具，以便利用健康情況檢查，例如負載平衡器、 服務探索和其他人所預期的行為相容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-115">This is compatible with the behavior expected by current infrastructural tooling that utilize health checks, such as load-balancers, service discoveries, and others.</span></span>

### <a name="enable-a-health-endpoint"></a><span data-ttu-id="cb437-116">啟用健康情況端點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-116">Enable a health endpoint</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="cb437-117">有兩種方式，來指定如何公開健康情況端點，並發佈 WCF 服務健全狀況資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-117">There are two ways to specify how to expose the health endpoint and publish WCF service health information:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="cb437-118">使用組態檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-118">By using a configuration file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-119">例如：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-119">For example:</span></span>

   ```xml
   <behaviors>
     <serviceBehaviors>
       <behavior name="DefaultBehavior">
         <serviceHealth httpGetEnabled="true"/>
       </behavior>
     </serviceBehaviors>
   </behaviors>
   ```

- <span data-ttu-id="cb437-120">以程式設計的方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-120">Programatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb437-121">下列程式碼片段會使用C#來公開健康情況端點：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb437-121">The following code fragment uses C# to expose the health endpoint:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    ServiceHost host = new ServiceHost(typeof(Service1),
        new Uri("http://jconde-dev1:81/Service1"));
    ServiceHealthBehavior healthBehavior =
                host.Description.Behaviors.Find<ServiceHealthBehavior>();
    if (healthBehavior == null)
    {
        healthBehavior = new ServiceHealthBehavior();
    }
    //healthBehavior.HttpGetEnabled = false;
    //healthBehavior.HttpsGetEnabled = false;
    host.Description.Behaviors.Add(healthBehavior);
    ```
